sequenceDiagram
  participant HA as Home Assistant
  participant A as Orchestrator
  participant Y as YOLO Perception
  participant V as VLM (on-demand)
  participant M as SQLite Memory
  participant L as JSONL Logger

  HA->>A: request: analyze_bedroom
  A->>Y: get latest detections + snapshot pointer
  Y-->>A: detections summary

  alt uncertain / needs semantics
    A->>V: call VLM with snapshot (only now)
    V-->>A: structured analysis (bed/clothes/desk/etc.)
  end

  A->>M: store episodic summary + pointers (no raw images by default)
  A->>L: log decision + outputs
  A-->>HA: response: concise summary + suggested actions (optional)
